685
00:57:35,738 --> 00:57:36,418
Councilor Callahan.

686
00:57:39,373 --> 00:57:45,114
I have attended the Boston Glory events, and I have eaten trolley dogs, and I have to highly recommend it for everyone.

687
00:57:46,695 --> 00:57:48,815
I'm excited personally to approve of this.

688
00:57:50,735 --> 00:57:51,015
Great.

